data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful home nestled in the countryside. With over 6 mostly wooded acres. Property has a large detached garage with a new large pole barn attached. The home has a screened patio overlooking the property. This home has two levels of living space with two kitchens. It has 6 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms The home was updated with new metal roofs. Home also has updated the windows, HVAC system and well pump. Enjoy all the fall colors this homes property has to offer.
